title: Chicken Ukrops- Jada
directions: Combine crushed stuffing, parmesan cheese and chervil. Dip chicken in
melted margarine, then roll in stuffing mixture.
Bake at 375 degrees for35-40 mins. Cover with aluminum foil for the first 20 mins.
After removing foil, turn the chicken and bake for remaining time.
When finished, squeeze fresh lemon juice over chicken.
ingredients: 1 c Pepperidge Farm herb stuffing, crushed
